## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="bc7b1-102">在  <xref:System.IO.FileSystemWatcher>，當您會收到通知的檔案變更，這些緩衝區之元件中的變更會建立並傳遞至應用程式發展介面 (Api) 的系統存放區。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bc7b1-102">In a <xref:System.IO.FileSystemWatcher>, when you are notified of file changes, the system stores those changes in a buffer the component creates and passes to the Application Programming Interfaces (APIs).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bc7b1-103">如果在短時間內有許多變更，緩衝區可以輕鬆地溢位，導致擲回例外狀況，這基本上會遺失所有變更。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bc7b1-103">If there are many changes in a short time, the buffer can easily overflow, resulting in an exception being thrown, which essentially loses all changes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bc7b1-104">若要防止緩衝區溢位，請使用<xref:System.IO.FileSystemWatcher.NotifyFilter%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>和<xref:System.IO.FileSystemWatcher.IncludeSubdirectories%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性篩選掉不必要的變更通知。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bc7b1-104">To keep the buffer from overflowing, use the <xref:System.IO.FileSystemWatcher.NotifyFilter%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> and <xref:System.IO.FileSystemWatcher.IncludeSubdirectories%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> properties to filter out your unwanted change notifications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bc7b1-105">您也可以透過 <xref:System.IO.FileSystemWatcher.InternalBufferSize%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 屬性增加內部緩衝區的大小。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bc7b1-105">You can also increase the size of the internal buffer through the <xref:System.IO.FileSystemWatcher.InternalBufferSize%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bc7b1-106">不過，增加緩衝區的大小是昂貴，所以讓緩衝區越小越好。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bc7b1-106">However, increasing the size of the buffer is expensive, so keep the buffer as small as possible.</span></span>  
  
   
  
